<%# app/views/training_enrollment_mailer/applicant_confirmation.html.erb %>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; background: #f5f5f5; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #1A1A1A; color: #FAF8F5; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #C9A227; }
    .header p { margin: 10px 0 0; opacity: 0.8; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; background: #ffffff; }
    .greeting { font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .program-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A1A 0%, #2a2a2a 100%); color: #FAF8F5; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center; }
    .program-box h3 { color: #C9A227; margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .program-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 20px; }
    .next-steps { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; }
    .next-steps h3 { margin: 0 0 15px; color: #1A1A1A; }
    .next-steps ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    .next-steps li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .cta { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
    .cta a { display: inline-block; background: #C9A227; color: #1A1A1A; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 13px; }
    .social { margin: 20px 0; }
    .social a { margin: 0 10px; color: #666; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>363 Photography</h1>
      <p>Photography & Editing Training</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Hi <%= @enrollment.first_name %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for your interest in our Photography & Editing Training Program! We're excited that you've taken the first step towards mastering the art of visual storytelling.</p>

      <div class="program-box">
        <h3>Program Selected</h3>
        <p><%= @enrollment.program_name %></p>
      </div>

      <p>We've received your application and our team will review it shortly. You can expect to hear from us within <strong>24 hours</strong>.</p>

      <div class="next-steps">
        <h3>What happens next?</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Review:</strong> Our team will review your application</li>
          <li><strong>Contact:</strong> We'll call or email you to discuss the program details</li>
          <li><strong>Schedule:</strong> We'll help you choose a class schedule that works for you</li>
          <li><strong>Payment:</strong> We'll share payment options including installment plans</li>
          <li><strong>Start:</strong> Begin your photography journey!</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>In the meantime, follow us on social media to see the amazing work our students create:</p>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/363photography.ng">Follow Us on Instagram</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email or call us directly.</p>

      <p>
        Warm regards,<br>
        <strong>The 363 Photography Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social">
        <a href="#">Instagram</a> |
        <a href="#">Facebook</a> |
        <a href="#">YouTube</a>
      </div>
      <p>363 Photography<br>
      Lagos, Nigeria</p>
      <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #999;">You received this email because you applied for our training program.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
